quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  6,60,"“Iye ndiyemwe amakupatsani imfa (yatulo) nthawi yausiku, ndipo amadziwa zimene mwachita masana, kenako amakudzutsani mmenemo kuti ikwane nthawi yanu yoikidwa (yofera); kenako kwa Iye ndiko kobwerera kwanu, nadzakuuzani zimene munkachita"
  6,61,"“Iye ndi M’gonjesi pa akapolo Ake ndipo amakutumizirani (angelo) osunga, (olemba zochita zanu); kufikira mmodzi wanu imfa ikamdzera, angelo athuwo amampatsa imfa, ndipo iwo sanyozera (ntchito yawo)"
  6,62,"“Kenako adzabwezedwa kwa Allah, Mbuye wawo Woona. Dziwani kuti kuweruza Nkwake. Iye Ngwachangu powerengera kuposa owerengera (onse)"
  6,63,"“Nena: “Kodi ndani amakupulumutsani m’masautso a pamtunda ndi panyanja?” Mumampempha modzichepetsa ndi motsitsa mawu (kuti): “Ngati atipulumutsa m’mazunzo awa, ndithudi tidzakhala mwa othokoza.”"
  6,64,"“Nena: “Allah ndi Yemwe amakupulumutsani ku zimenezo ndi ku masautso a mtundu uliwonse. Kenako inu mukumphatikiza ndi mafano"
  6,65,"“Nena: “Iye Ngokhoza kukutumizirani chilango kuchokera pamwamba panu kapena pansi pa miyendo yanu, kapena kudzetsa chisokonezo nkukhala magulumagulu (osamvana), ndipo (akhoza) kuwalawitsa ena a inu chilango cha mtopola wa ena.” Taona momwe tikufotokozera zizindikiro kuti iwo azindikire"
  6,66,"“Koma anthu ako aitsutsa iyo (Qur’an) pomwe ili yoona. Nena: “Ine sindili muyang’anili pa inu.”"
  6,67,“Nkhani iliyonse (yomwe yatchulidwa apa) ili ndi nthawi yake yodziwika (yofikira). Ndipo posachedwapa mudziwa (izi)
  6,68,"“Ndipo (iwe Msilamu weniweni) ukawaona omwe akuchita chipongwe ndi Ayah Zathu, apatuke mpaka anene nkhani ina. Ndipo ngati satana atakuiwalitsa, (nkukhala nawo pomwe iwo akukambirana zotere), choncho, pambuyo pokumbukira usakhale pamodzi ndi anthu ochita zoipa"